nentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"ControlItemComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"borders (from "},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"),  colors (from "},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")  and spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider/sizeErrorIcon":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sizeErrorIcon"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"SizeSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDS